~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : accreq                                    ~FTPODnuts
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : accreq <email address>

   This command is the final stage in auto-promote for users wishing to
   create an account here.  The idea is that they give their email address
   so the sysop can mail them to confirm their identity.

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

